# Usage

## Preparations

Provide your cross file (or adjust the example in armv7.txt):

* toolchain
* sys_root
* pkg_config_libdir

Export device ip to DEVICE_IP, if user is not root, adjust the user as well (and make sure the user has permission to access /dev/dri/card0).

## Execute

* meson builddir --cross-file armv7.txt
* ./vblank.sh